        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-08-10T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-08-10T19:00:00-05:00" n="1018" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1018">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">693.0031/7–849: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Tihwa</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Paxton</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-08-10T20:00:00-04:00">August 10, 1949—8 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>112. Re urtel 181, Jul 8. After inquiry Dept unable suggest any Amer at Lanchow
                    suitable for work mentioned. However further consideration this question,
                    including possible appointment outside <pb facs="1071" n="1061" xml:id="pg_1061"/> person, would need await clarification mil and communications situation,
                    reportedly deteriorating, in that area.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
